                        <a href="/Plugins/ShopPlugin/UI/UserInfo.aspx" class="at_tab_i at_current">基本资料</a>
                        <a href="/Plugins/ShopPlugin/UI/ContractInfo.aspx" class="at_tab_i">联系方式</a> <a href="/Plugins/ShopPlugin/UI/PhotoUpload.aspx"
